Description: The Visual C++ Redistributable Packages install run-time components that are required to run C++ applications built using Visual Studio 2017.
PSPreInstall:
$SW = gci "HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Wow6432Node\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\" | foreach { gp $_.PSPath } | select UninstallString,DisplayName | where { $_.DisplayName -like "Microsoft Visual C++ 2017 Redistributable (x86) - *" }
$SW | % { start-process $_.UninstallString.Split("/")[0].replace("`"", "") -ArgumentList '/uninstall /quiet /norestart' -Wait }
